cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.DS, cs.RO 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning and Monte Carlo Tree Search (MCTS) planning algorithm, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and robotics (cs.RO). The paper's title and abstract also mention "discounting," which is a common concept in reinforcement learning, further supporting the likelihood of cs.AI and cs.LG as the most likely sub-categories.
